<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>百词斩用户信息查询</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>百词斩用户信息查询</h1>
            <p>输入BCZID获取用户详细信息</p>
            <a href="/logout" class="logout-btn">退出登录</a>
        </header>

        <main>
            <form id="search-form" class="search-form">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="bczid">BCZID</label>
                    <input type="text" id="bczid" name="bczid" placeholder="请输入用户BCZID" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">查询</button>
            </form>
        </main>

        <script type="module">
            import { checkAuth } from '/js/cookie.js';
            checkAuth();

            document.getElementById('search-form').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                const bczid = document.getElementById('bczid').value;
                window.location.href = '/user/' + bczid;
            });
        </script>

        <footer>
            <div class="version-info">
                <h3>v2.0版本上线啦！</h3>
                <ul class="update-content">
                    <li>更新内核，获取更多信息</li>
                    <li>更新UI适应手机比例</li>
                    <li>新后端，高并发，高性能</li>
                    <li>修复已知bug</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <p>&copy; 2025 百词斩用户信息查询系统</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
